1
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:09,289
Miss, do you remember the assassin from that day?

2
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:10,600
We have a lead.

3
00:01:10,600 --> 00:01:13,440
A year ago, the Song Army fell at the Qilian Mountain border.

4
00:01:13,440 --> 00:01:14,520
They were nearly wiped out.

5
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,800
But during my investigation,

6
00:01:15,800 --> 00:01:18,480
I found a squad of a dozen men went missing.

7
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:21,280
They were not in the main formation at the time.

8
00:01:21,560 --> 00:01:23,680
Is there a record in the military registry?

9
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:26,080
They were ordered to seek reinforcements.

10
00:01:26,160 --> 00:01:27,680
And haven't been heard from since.

11
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,039
But the situation was chaotic then.

12
00:01:29,039 --> 00:01:30,280
So it wasn't investigated immediately.

13
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:31,440
When you asked me to reopen the case,

14
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,800
I discovered this record.

15
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,120
If they are alive,

16
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,240
even if it's just one person,

17
00:01:35,240 --> 00:01:36,479
I must find them.

18
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:38,240
If they are dead,

19
00:01:38,520 --> 00:01:40,680
I must know where they are buried.

20
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:51,720
Hey, Daylily.

21
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:54,920
We are officially married now.

22
00:01:56,039 --> 00:01:57,000
Look.

23
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:01,440
As they say, the husband is the wife's guide.

24
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,800
So,

25
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,800
have you seen any other wife

26
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:08,080
who doesn't give her husband some allowance?

27
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:10,960
Asking for a hundred taels isn't too much, is it?

28
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,220
You want money?

29
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,800
Sure.

30
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:17,040
A hundred taels?

31
00:02:17,040 --> 00:02:19,240
Do you think the Marquis Manor is a bank?

32
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,900
A real man knows when to yield.

33
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:32,440
I'm just a bit short on cash lately.

34
00:02:32,440 --> 00:02:33,400
Short on cash?

35
00:02:33,640 --> 00:02:36,200
Chaohua asked me for cosmetic money again.

36
00:02:36,280 --> 00:02:37,640
As her older brother,

37
00:02:37,760 --> 00:02:39,280
I can't just ignore her, can I?

38
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,360
A brother giving his sister cosmetic money.

39
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:42,040
Reasonable.

40
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:42,800
Right?

41
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,600
Sister-in-law.

42
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:48,280
Chaohua.

43
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,920
Did you hear what your brother just said?

44
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:54,000
I heard you're short on cosmetic money lately.

45
00:02:54,160 --> 00:02:55,090
Sister-in-law,

46
00:02:55,120 --> 00:02:56,079
since you married into the family,

47
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,520
you've managed the household perfectly.

48
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:59,000
Our Marquis Manor lacks nothing.

49
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:01,120
What my brother just said was all a lie.

50
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,680
Bai Chaohua, you traitor!

51
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,920
Young Master, bad news.

52
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:06,920
Miss Shen is here.

53
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:08,040
Shen Lingbo?

54
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,940
What is she doing here?

55
00:03:10,360 --> 00:03:11,160
You may leave.

56
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:15,340
Sister.

57
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,040
Miss Song, we parted in a hurry that day.

58
00:03:21,360 --> 00:03:22,880
I didn't have time to thank you properly.

59
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,720
I have prepared a small gift today

60
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:26,120
as a token of my appreciation.

61
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:28,560
Peonies are also known as 'Parting'.

62
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:31,840
Miss Shen, this gift is truly unique.

63
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:33,840
Miss Song knows her flowers.

64
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:35,360
But you've misunderstood.

65
00:03:35,360 --> 00:03:37,720
I just think peonies are peerlessly beautiful.

66
00:03:37,720 --> 00:03:39,720
They suit you perfectly, Miss Song.

67
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:42,960
It's just a pity their blooming season is so short.

68
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:45,290
Miss Shen, why not speak your mind?

69
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,760
Marriage is like a peony.

70
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,410
It requires constant care.

71
00:03:50,079 --> 00:03:52,540
If you want to keep this marriage, Miss Song,

72
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,440
don't let anyone take advantage of a weak spot.

73
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:57,680
Are you advising me to guard against others,

74
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:59,410
or are you hinting at yourself?

75
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:05,160
Sometimes, it's not good for a woman to be too confident.

76
00:04:05,640 --> 00:04:07,720
Thank you for the reminder, Miss Shen.

77
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:08,650
You're welcome.

78
00:04:14,440 --> 00:04:15,760
What did that woman come here for?

79
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:18,360
Spouting all that nonsense. What did she mean?

80
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,360
I don't know.

81
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,500
I really don't.

82
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:26,940
Why did you kick me?

83
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,680
Brother, you're done for.

84
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:35,680
I think you've offended my sister-in-law.

85
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:38,360
Go away.

86
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,840
Don't talk nonsense.

87
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,520
Why are you still standing there?

88
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,980
Go apologize to your wife.

89
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:48,640
Why should I apologize?

90
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,760
I didn't do anything wrong.

91
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,240
You think you did nothing wrong?

92
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:52,520
Shen Lingbo even sent flowers to the door,

93
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,000
saying those sarcastic things.

94
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,720
How is my sister-in-law supposed to deal with that?

95
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,840
I didn't ask her to send flowers.

96
00:04:58,000 --> 00:05:00,640
Anyway, you and this Shen Lingbo,

97
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,720
your relationship is ambiguous.

98
00:05:02,720 --> 00:05:04,880
I told you, I have nothing to do with her.

99
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:07,000
Can I stop her from doing what she wants?

100
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:10,000
Then why didn't you make your stance clear right then?

101
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,880
And now you're acting aggrieved?

102
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:14,880
Weren't you the one begging me back then

103
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:17,360
to help you marry Song Xuan?

104
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,890
Your Highness, Your Highness.

105
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,060
Your Highness.

106
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,840
I heard

107
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:26,120
Prince Duan wants to match you with General Song's daughter.

108
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,800
She's just the daughter of a brute.

109
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,760
If it weren't for my father,

110
00:05:28,760 --> 00:05:30,520
why would I have anything to do with her?

111
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,360
Watch your words, Your Highness.

112
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,960
To hell with watching my words.

113
00:05:33,960 --> 00:05:35,920
I'd like to see how long the Song family

114
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,600
can last on the battlefield.

115
00:05:47,360 --> 00:05:48,440
What are you doing, Bai Manchuan?

116
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:50,440
I was just drinking my wine

117
00:05:50,440 --> 00:05:52,640
when I heard a dog barking,

118
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,810
so I came in to check.

119
00:05:54,280 --> 00:05:58,120
I didn't expect it to be you, Prince Duan's heir.

120
00:05:58,120 --> 00:05:59,200
Who are you calling a dog?

121
00:05:59,200 --> 00:05:59,880
You're the dog.

122
00:05:59,880 --> 00:06:01,120
Your whole family are dogs.

123
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,680
He said I was a wolf last night.

124
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:04,880
I wasn't talking about you, naturally.

125
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:10,360
General Song's family is loyal and devoted,

126
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,480
yet here you are spouting nonsense,

127
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,600
judging his daughter.

128
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:18,760
Your behavior isn't even worthy of a dog.

129
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:21,280
Song Xuan is about to marry me.

130
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:21,720
Whatever I say

131
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:22,760
is my family's business.

132
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:24,360
It's not your place to judge.

133
00:06:25,280 --> 00:06:27,360
The Emperor hasn't granted the marriage yet,

134
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:30,290
and you're already acting like Miss Song's husband.

135
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:33,680
You really are full of yourself.

136
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,480
Because I want to.

137
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,560
Bai Manchuan,

138
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:37,400
you dare to go against me?

139
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:38,880
Then let's settle this.

140
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:44,920
Bai Manchuan!

141
00:06:44,920 --> 00:06:45,840
Let go of me!

142
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:46,240
Bai Manchuan!

143
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:46,840
Yuan Huai!

144
00:06:46,840 --> 00:06:48,400
Do you really think I'm afraid of you?

145
00:06:48,400 --> 00:06:49,080
Let me go!

146
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:49,720
Gentlemen,

147
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,920
calm down, calm down.

148
00:06:51,000 --> 00:06:52,400
Stop fighting.

149
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:54,080
Baihua Pavilion is a place for fun,

150
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:55,840
not for fighting.

151
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,560
Young Master Bai, Young Master Bai,

152
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,160
stop fighting.

153
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,760
Someone's going to get hurt.

154
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:03,320
Bai Manchuan!

155
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,760
You dare hit my handsome face?

156
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,960
This isn't over!

157
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,960
Stop!

158
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,160
Come here.

159
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,040
I heard

160
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:29,760
you got into a fight with Prince Duan's heir at Baihua Pavilion yesterday.

161
00:07:29,760 --> 00:07:31,400
So what if I did?

162
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:37,040
Someone accused you in court of violent assault.

163
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,880
What did His Majesty say?

164
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:41,210
He's not going to throw me in prison, is he?

165
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,400
Scared now?

166
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,760
What am I scared of?

167
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,640
I was speaking up for justice.

168
00:07:47,760 --> 00:07:48,640
If I had to do it again,

169
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:50,570
I'd still beat that shameless man.

170
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:53,159
She'd be better off marrying me than him.

171
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,159
You like her?

172
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:02,880
So I really did say that.

173
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,760
You...

174
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,560
Husband, why are you still standing here?

175
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,890
Go back to your studies.

176
00:08:21,760 --> 00:08:23,360
I have something to explain.

177
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,320
Explain what?

178
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,170
Why are you dodging?

179
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,720
Guilty conscience?

180
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:33,020
My relationship with Shen Lingbo isn't what you think.

181
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,760
I have nothing to do with Shen Lingbo.

182
00:08:39,440 --> 00:08:40,970
Then why are you panicking?

183
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,159
Over ten years ago,

184
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,840
when Lord Shen Zhao went to Jiangnan to take office,

185
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,360
he took a fancy to Shen Lingbo's birth mother.

186
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,040
She got pregnant.

187
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:47,640
But she didn't dare say anything.

188
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:49,240
Later, he was promoted and returned to the Capital.

189
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:50,680
She was afraid of ruining his career,

190
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:52,810
so she gave birth to Shen Lingbo alone.

191
00:08:53,880 --> 00:08:54,640
Get to the point.

192
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:56,080
Later, when Madam Shen found out,

193
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,560
she sent assassins to slaughter her entire family.

194
00:08:57,560 --> 00:09:00,160
Her mother told Shen Lingbo the truth right before she died.

195
00:09:00,160 --> 00:09:03,200
Later, Shen Lingbo traveled a thousand miles alone to find her father.

196
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:05,560
She was almost sold into Baihua Pavilion.

197
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,240
Then you must have...

198
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,480
played the hero saving the damsel.

199
00:09:11,480 --> 00:09:13,600
I just stepped in when I saw injustice.

200
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:16,840
On Shen Zhao's birthday, I arranged a blood test for them.

201
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,080
But that day at Baihua Pavilion,

202
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,600
I clearly saw you two coming out of the same room.

203
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,800
I didn't do anything.

204
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:27,080
I probably didn't...

205
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,640
Then towards her,

206
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:35,080
didn't you feel anything at all?

207
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:39,800
I'm a very virtuous man, okay?

208
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,640
Since you're a good person,

209
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:48,240
you deserve to be punished even more.

210
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,440
Huanghuacai.

211
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:50,360
You...

212
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:55,200
W-W-What are you doing?

213
00:09:55,880 --> 00:09:57,680
Husband, just study hard.
